"High on You" – 4:48
"Strong Girl" (Steve Jones, Pop) – 5:04
"Tom Tom" – 3:17
"Easy Rider" (Jones, Pop) – 4:54
"Power & Freedom" (Jones, Pop) – 3:53
"Lowdown" – 4:30
"Instinct" – 4:12
"Tuff Baby" – 4:27
"Squarehead" (Jones, Pop) – 5:06

